# MCP Server Environment Configuration
# Copy this file to remove .sample extension and update values

# Server Configuration
PORT=8080

# Service URLs - Update these for your environment
# For local development:
TASK_SERVICE_URL=http://localhost:8081
CALENDAR_SERVICE_URL=http://localhost:8082
WEATHER_SERVICE_URL=http://localhost:8083

# For Kubernetes deployment (uncomment these):
# TASK_SERVICE_URL=http://task-service:8081
# CALENDAR_SERVICE_URL=http://calendar-service:8082
# WEATHER_SERVICE_URL=http://weather-service:8083

# Development Settings
LOG_LEVEL=info
DEBUG=false

# Usage:
# 1. Copy this file: cp config/mcp-server.env.sample config/mcp-server.env
# 2. Edit config/mcp-server.env with your values
# 3. Source it: source config/mcp-server.env
# 4. Run the service: cd services/mcp-server && go run main.go